snippet.title: Apple IIGS Game: LemminGS (1996 Psygnosis)
snippet.description:
LemminGS is an port of Lemmings for the Apple IIGS. This version of the game has 92 Levels, unlike the original official 16bit computer versions which have 120.

Please like this video and subscribe to my channel for more great retro content.

Good retro gaming channel @Shadowserg
